  "description": {
    "zh": "一个自称Mechanic的神秘人最近来了我这里。他口风很严，平时不怎么说话，你一定听过他。他什么都没买，只是说他对燃料感兴趣。我记得Ultra那里有些燃料罐，在那种带着德国国旗的拖车上。长话短说，去用信标把它们标记上，我好给Mechanic搞一些燃料，他答应给我个好价钱。",
    "en": "Hey, got something interesting for you, listen. A certain guy dropped by recently, goes by the name of Mechanic. A tight-lipped type, keeps silent all the time, you must have heard about him. Didn't buy anything but he said he's interested in fuel. And I remember that there were fuel tanks near Ultra, strapped onto the trucks, the ones with the German flag. I want you to go there and mark the fuel tanks with beacons. I’ll send some fuel to Mechanic, he promised to pay well. You'll have your cut too, don't worry."
  },
